ed by tyranny is unfit to govern a free people therefore we declare that these united colonies are free and independent states absolved from allegiance to the british crown they have full power to levy war conclude peace form alliances and establish commerce with firm reliance on divine providence we pledge our lives fortunes and sacred honor",
